{"metadata":{"url":"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://p.udn.com.tw/upf/2020_wj/noimg_cid121106_4.jpg&w=480&q=75","titleLink":"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121251/9463718","title":"一百枚大银圆(上)","paragraph":"那年我六岁，身穿白底带有各种颜色花朵图案的洋布连衣裙，后脑勺左右扎上一对羊角辫，辫子上用大红的绸丝带系了两个蝴蝶结，肩膀上斜挎一个红色、小巧玲珑的皮包包。在镜子前照了照，觉得自己好美呀，得意得不行。...","cateLink":"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/cate/arts","cateTitle":"艺文","time":{"art_roc_time":"2026-05-02 14:00:00","date":"2026-05-02 02:00","modify_time":1777246511501},"slotname":"list_彭丽荷","content_level":"開放閱讀"},"title":"一百枚大银圆(上)","date":"2026-05-02 02:00 ET","author":"彭丽荷","url":"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121251/9463718?zh-cn"}
